# Project-mode parity examples (parity/[0-9][0-9][0-9]-*) clone an
# external repository on demand into a .checkout/<ref>/ slot. The
# checkout is gigabytes of source code we never want to commit — CI
# re-clones it dynamically on every run.
.checkout/
